===Etymology===
From {{etyl|NL.|en}} {{term|lang=la|camera obscura||dark chamber}}, because the first cameras used a [[pinhole]] and a dark room; from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|lang=la|camera||chamber or bedchamber}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|καμάρα||tr=kamara|anything with an arched cover, a covered carriage or boat, a vaulted chamber, a vault|tr=kamara|lang=grc}}.

